    <date day="05" month="June" year="2002"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo describes a new RFC 2822 message header, "Message-Context".  This header provides information about the context and presentation characteristics of a message.  A receiving user agent (UA) may use this information as a hint to optimally present the message. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
	 </t>
    </abstract>
